1. Home Page

Goal: Make a strong first impression and clearly show what you do.
Sections:

Hero Banner:
High-quality image/video of your best furniture (office desk, school benches, home cabinets).
Headline: “Custom Furniture for Home, Office & School”
Call-to-action (CTA) buttons: “View Gallery” / “Request a Quote”
Services Snapshot:
Small section with icons or images for Home, Office, School furniture.
Quick link to full portfolio.
Why Choose Us:
3–5 bullets: Custom design, premium materials, fast delivery, experience years, local service.
Featured Projects / Carousel:
Show 3–5 best works with “View More” linking to Portfolio page.
Testimonials / Client Feedback:
Rotating quotes or video reviews from satisfied clients.
CTA Section:
“Get Your Custom Quote Today!” → links to request form or WhatsApp chat.
2. Portfolio / Gallery Page

Goal: Showcase your work to build trust.

Sections:

Filterable Gallery:
Categories: Home / Office / School / Outdoor / Custom
High-resolution images of finished products.
Project Details Modal:
Click an image → opens:
Product name
Materials used
Dimensions
Short story (if relevant)
Before & After Section:
Show transformations, e.g., old furniture → custom redesign.
CTA:
“Like this design? Request a Custom Quote!”
3. Custom Order / Request a Quote Page

Goal: Let clients submit their custom requirements easily.

Form Fields:

Name
Contact: Phone, Email, WhatsApp
Type of furniture: Home / Office / School
Dimensions (optional or guided)
Material preference: Wood type, finish
Upload Design/Sketch (optional)
Additional Notes

Extra Features:

Auto-response email confirming request.
Link to WhatsApp chat for faster connection.
Optional price calculator: small tool to give ballpark cost based on furniture type & size.
4. Shop / E-commerce Page

Goal: Sell ready-made furniture online.

Features:

Product catalog with images, descriptions, price, and “Add to Cart” button.
Categories: Office Chairs, Desks, Cabinets, School Furniture, Home Furniture.
Product page details: Materials, Dimensions, Delivery Time, Warranty.
Cart & checkout: Payment via UPI, card, or COD.
Order tracking for clients (optional).
5. About Us Page

Goal: Build credibility and connect with clients.

Sections:

Your story: How you started, experience.
Workshop / Team photos.
Your mission & values: Quality, custom designs, customer satisfaction.
Certifications / awards (if any).
6. Blog / Tips Section (Optional but Powerful)

Goal: Boost SEO and show expertise.

Furniture care tips
Office ergonomics guides
Home storage hacks
Custom design trends
7. Contact Page

Goal: Make it super easy to reach you.

Sections:

Phone, Email, WhatsApp button
Google Maps location (if you have a workshop/showroom)
Quick contact form (Name, Phone, Message)
8. Extra Features
Live Chat / WhatsApp Integration: Instant client communication.
SEO Optimization: Use keywords like “custom furniture [your city]”
Mobile-friendly: Most people will check on mobile phones.
Social Media Links: Instagram/Facebook for photos and stories.
Customer Login (optional): For tracking custom order progress.